OL,4,CPM says education is universal cure
OL,5,Cdespite aid row
OL,6, Investing in education in some of the
OL,7, world's poorest countries is the
OL,8, "single best investment we can make in
OL,9, the future of humanity", Boris Johnson
OL,10, has told an education summit in London.
OL,12,FThe Global Partnership for Education
OL,13,Fraised more than $4bn (#2.9bn) from
OL,14,Fpledges, including #430m from the UK.
OL,16,FNobel Prize winner Malala Yousafzai
OL,17,Ftold the summit girls in particular
OL,18,Ffaced an "education crisis".
OL,20,FBut charities warned the UK's aid cuts
OL,21,Fhad harmed fundraising.
